    },
    {
      "word": "nachgeben",
      "target_language": "german",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Sie wollte zuerst nicht, aber am Ende musste sie ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "nachgeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "is_target": false
            }
          ],
          "english": "She didn't want to at first, but in the end, she had to give in."
        },
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Der alte Stuhl würde bestimmt ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "nachgeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", wenn sich jemand daraufsetzt.",
              "is_target": false
            }
          ],
          "english": "The old chair would definitely give way if someone sat on it."
        },
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Manchmal muss man einfach dem Druck ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "nachgeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", um Frieden zu haben.",
              "is_target": false
            }
          ],
          "english": "Sometimes you just have to give in to the pressure to have peace."
        },
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Der Boden schien ein wenig ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "nachzugeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", als ich darüber ging.",
              "is_target": false
            }
          ],
          "english": "The floor seemed to give a little when I walked over it."
        },
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Er weigerte sich, in der Diskussion auch nur einen Zentimeter ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "nachzugeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "is_target": false
            }
          ],
          "english": "He refused to concede even an inch in the discussion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "word": "zugeben",
      "target_language": "german",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "fragments": [
            {
              "text": "Ich muss ",
              "is_target": false
            },
            {
              "text": "zugeben",
              "is_target": true
            },
            {
              "text": ", dass ich einen Fehler gemacht habe.",
              "is_target": false
            }
